data.description: **Sellers may require rent-back until 07/15/24.** Almost New Gem located in the Safe Haven Development! Stunning 3 Bed, 2 Bath, 2 Car Garage on 0.140 Acres. Welcome home to this captivating retreat that has been well cared for! Nestled on a generous 0.140-acre lot, this charming abode boasts modern comforts and style, perfect for those seeking a blend of luxury and coziness. This impeccable home features: 3 Bedrooms: Spacious rooms for rest and relaxation. 2 Bathrooms: Stylish and convenient for your lifestyle, with great natural light. The kitchen has beautiful cabinets and counter tops. The primary suite is a great size with a large closet. Schedule a showing today, because this wont last long. Buyer & Buyers Agent to verify all information. Water Softener included. (Escrow has been pre-opened, email or call for contact information.) Loan is assumable, contact listing agent for more info.
